\c 8
\s Ukukhaliswa kwempondo eziyisikhombisa
\p
\v 1 Lapho selivule\x + 6.1.\x* uphawu lwesikhombisa\x + 5.1.\x*, kwaba khona ukuthula ezulwini okungaba yingxenye yehola.
\v 2 Ngasengibona ingilosi eziyisikhombisa\x + 1.4.\x* ezazimi phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + Luka 1.19. Mat. 18.10.\x*, njalo kwanikelwa kizo impondo\x + 1 Lan. 15.24. Levi 25.9,10.\x* eziyisikhombisa.
\v 3 Kwasekufika enye ingilosi, yasisima elathini, ilomganu wegolide wokutshisela impepha\x + Heb. 9.4.\x*, yasiphiwa impepha enengi, ukuze i\add yi\add*nikele lemikhuleko\f + \fk iyinikele lemikhuleko: \fl kumbe, \fq iyengezelele emikhulekweni.\f* yabo bonke abangcwele\x + 5.8.\x* phezu kwelathi legolide eliphambi kwesihlalo sobukhosi\x + Eks. 30.1,3. Isam. 8.5. 9.13; 11.1.\x*.
\v 4 Lentuthu yempepha yenyuka lemikhuleko yabangcwele\x + 5.8.\x* esandleni sengilosi phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + Seb. 10.4.\x*.
\v 5 Ingilosi yasithatha umganu wokutshisela impepha\x + Heb. 9.4.\x*, yasiwugcwalisa ngomlilo\x + Levi 16.12.\x* welathi\x + Eks. 30.1,3.Isam.5.9.13; 11.1.\x*, yasi\add wu\add*phosela emhlabeni\x + 8.8.\x*; kwasekusiba khona amazwi lemidumo lemibane\x + 4.5.\x* lokuzamazama komhlaba\x + 1 Kho. 19.11. Isam. 11.19. Hlu. 5.4. Seb. 4.31. Isam. 6.12.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kwathi ingilosi eziyisikhombisa ezazilempondo eziyisikhombisa zazilungiselela ukuze zizikhalise.
\p
\v 7 Ingilosi yokuqala yasilukhalisa uphondo, kwasekusiba khona isiqhotho\x + Hez. 38.22.\x*\x + 11.19; 16.21.\x* lomlilo kuhlanganiswe legazi\x + Hez. 38.22.\x*, kwasekuphoselwa emhlabeni\x + 16.2.\x*; lengxenye yesithathu\x + 9.15,18; 12.4.\x* yezihlahla yatshiswa\x + 9.4.\x*\x + Isa. 2.13; 10.18.\x*, labo bonke utshani obuluhlaza batshiswa\x + 9.4.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Ingilosi yesibili yasilukhalisa uphondo; kwasekuphoselwa olwandle okunjengentaba enkulu evutha umlilo\x + Jer. 51.25.\x*\x + 8.8.\x*\x + 16.3.\x*. Lengxenye yesithathu yolwandle\x + 16.3.\x* yaba ligazi\x + Eks. 7.17,19. Isam. 11.6.\x*;
\v 9 kwasekusifa ingxenye yesithathu yezidalwa eziselwandle\x + 16.3.\x* ezilempilo\x + 16.3.\x*, lengxenye yesithathu yemikhumbi yachithwa\x + Isa. 2.16.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Ingilosi yesithathu yasilukhalisa uphondo, kwasekusiwa ezulwini inkanyezi enkulu\x + 9.1. Isa. 14.12. Isam. 6.13.\x* ibhebha njengesibane\x + 4.5.\x*, yasiwela phezu kwengxenye yesithathu yemifula, laphezu kwemithombo yamanzi\x + 16.4.\x*.
\v 11 Lebizo lenkanyezi lalithiwa nguMhlonyane\x + Dute. 29.18. Zaga 5.4. Ruthe 1.20.\x*; lengxenye yesithathu yamanzi yaba ngumhlonyane, labantu abanengi bafa ngamanzi, ngoba ayenziwe ababa\x + Jer. 8.14. Eks. 15.23.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Ingilosi yesine yasilukhalisa uphondo, kwasekutshaywa ingxenye yesithathu yelanga lengxenye yesithathu yenyanga lengxenye yesithathu yezinkanyezi\x + 6.12; 16.8. Mat. 24.29.\x*, ukuze kufiphazwe ingxenye yesithathu yazo, lengxenye yesithathu yemini ingakhanyi, lobusuku ngokunjalo.
\p
\v 13 Ngasengibona, ngasengisizwa ingilosi\x + 14.6.\x* eyodwa iphapha phakathi laphakathi kwezulu\x + 14.6.\x*\x + 19.17.\x*, isithi ngelizwi elikhulu: Maye, maye\x + 9.12; 11.14.\x*, maye kulabo\x + 12.12.\x* abakhileyo emhlabeni\x + 12.12.\x*\x + 3.10.\x*, kumazwi aseleyo empondo zengilosi ezintathu esezizakhala!
